{"tid":1469716,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急幫推］至今最少七百人被捕，付出左前途，我地可以為佢地付出多十秒嗎","createTime":"2019-08-14T02:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T03:08:40.000Z","uid":58883,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c33e5fde8045781f56d3bee0ba718db65d374345","tid":1469716,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:50:33.000Z","msg":"他們為了爭取自由被捕，你願意為他們用十秒簽署罷賣承諾嗎？請各位幫忙宣揚<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">逄星期日，五罷買</span></span></strong>理念，用我地小小力量齊齊救港！<br />\n呢個運動好需要你地齊手簽署，到時候我地就可以用２００萬人參與罷買，向政府施壓。<br />\n只需<span style=\"color: red;\">十秒</span><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">ＳＩＧＮ　ＵＰ　ＰＡＧＥ</span></strong>：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ORv5Zw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ORv5Zw&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0WbkIIQgOyZVEIOEDwMYbAQ%3D&h=74246ad7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ORv5Zw</a><br />\n請幫推廣傳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67980379_109233473768439_5568711878525321216_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_oc=AQncVoeRIRzHFZgrS6bQ_l_WbRdKPSHD8MJDZm6DlAAMHzrh0Y4QxP_5DNI7D8dV2RI&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=742ab26775359d12bd9b215ebc31ad62&amp;oe=5DDB0FDB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67980379_109233473768439_5568711878525321216_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_oc%3DAQncVoeRIRzHFZgrS6bQ_l_WbRdKPSHD8MJDZm6DlAAMHzrh0Y4QxP_5DNI7D8dV2RI%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D742ab26775359d12bd9b215ebc31ad62%26oe%3D5DDB0FDB&h=64f43496&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n#日五罷買 #SunFriByeBuy<br />\n#罷買救港 #ByeBuySaveHK<br />\n#全民罷買日 #ByeBuyDayHK"},{"pid":"66c786aefc3fdaf1aa7224b029b4ef20a1751354","tid":1469716,"uid":58883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:51:27.000Z","msg":"<strong>罷買內容（好簡單）</strong><br />\n1. 逄星期五、日不花費於日常必須以外的消費<br />\n2. 逄星期五、日不在外食 (上班人士午餐除非可以帶返否則難以避免，但晚餐回家進餐都十分有幫助)<br />\n3. 同時呼籲不光顧抵制清單內的企業，就算買日用品/其他消費都只幫襯良心/本土/外資企業<br />\n4. 呼籲推己及人, 例如絲打比仔仔約逢星期五、日出街食飯，同佢地講逄星期五、日罷買，或只揀良心企業<br />\n由上述基本概念，長遠減低整體消費。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>點解要罷買？</strong><br />\n政府漠視民意，官黑勾結，利用警黑合作／白色恐怖等下流手段打擊市民言論自由。然而政府對市民傷亡不聞不問，只談經濟，由此可見，經濟係向政府施壓既其中一個有效手段。我地希望令政府唔好再用下流手段，正面回應民間五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>罷買可以好有效</strong><br />\n如果香港有200萬人=1/4人口每星期少2日購物 = 1/4*2/7 = 少7%營業額，對鋪租貴既香港地，7%營業額分分鍾就等於商家既50%淨利。罷買唔係罷工, 幾個人唔返工對間公司連作可能無影響, 但香港咁多人, 只要集體真係唔買, 生意少左就係少左, 實有效果。<br />\n<br />\n罷買目的係令到香港經濟短期受影響，令社會各界開始不滿政府。更加有學者研究指出，罷買只需要全港252,000人集中一日不消費，經濟就會受到好大影響。 (BBC： The '3.5% rule:' How a small minority can change the world.)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>可以支持返良心小店嗎？</strong><br />\n罷買唔係希望大家苦行，亦唔係希望搞死所有商家。我地會配合其他藍黃店舖ＡＰＰ，呼籲大家將有必要既消費花係良心小店上，同時全面抵制奶共／黑心店。<br />\n長遠黎講我地目標係令到經濟受影響，搞死奶共／黑心店，黃店唔受影響甚至有正面影響。<br />\n自由篩 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1423228/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1423228/page/1</a><br />\n發夢罷食app <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1421345/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1421345/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>參與罷買者的好處</strong><br />\n1. 香港消費貴，養成罷買習慣減低消費，同時能夠建立良好儲蓄習慣<br />\n2. 儲錢捐助立場/其他僅有的中立新聞機構，保護新聞自由<br />\n3. 留錢幫助有需要人士<br />\n4. 留錢買保護裝備<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>點解揀星期日同五？</strong><br />\n我地相信一星期揀幾日，會比較容易令香港人持續實行。而星期日同五兩日係由１萬人既投票結果決定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港人有可能響應嗎？</strong><br />\n我地揀左每星期日同五 兩日去集體響應。相信呢２個月發生既事，加上互相影響提點下，香港人唔會再善忘。<br />\n<br />\nSo far Facebook/ig都見到好多人share我地既posters，特別係Working Class既反應好好，都成功係爸爸媽媽間廣傳。但係，最緊要都係你既參與同share。<br />\n（直擊養心殿午市營業狀況： <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1454146/page/1）\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1454146/page/1）</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>未來活動方向 </strong><br />\na. 陸續推動其他innovative既嚮應方法，如$50/day challenge<br />\nb. 配合其他人搞既活動，例如去商場涼冷氣<br />\nc. 配合其他組織，例如環保組織，共同將罷買概念輸出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/cfvAQNs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcfvAQNs.jpg&h=11e8f15b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/VaKt3Uh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVaKt3Uh.jpg&h=4a0328f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFACEBOOK PAGE <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/byebuydayhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbyebuydayhk%2F&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0WbkIIQgOyZVEIOEDwMYbAQ%3D&h=e26d5898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/byebuydayhk/</a><br />\nIG PAGE <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/byebuydayhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbyebuydayhk%2F&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0WbkIIQgOyZVEIOEDwMYbAQ%3D&h=9a7f4caf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/byebuydayhk/</a><br />\n罷買運動文字詳情 <a href=\"https://buyersstrike2019.wixsite.com/mysite\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuyersstrike2019.wixsite.com%2Fmysite&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0WbkIIQgOyZVEIOEDwMYbAQ%3D&h=f73db880\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://buyersstrike2019.wixsite.com/mysite</a><br />\n以前既ＰＯＳＴ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1441419/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1441419/page/1</a><br />\n金水ＦＢ ＰＯＳＴ <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/photos/a.233233693430128/2382386658514810/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FChanKamShui%2Fphotos%2Fa.233233693430128%2F2382386658514810%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0WbkIIQgOyZVEIOEDwMYbAQ%3D&h=89823124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/photos/a.233233693430128/2382386658514810/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"38f9dfe61b8a891276db7516344af705f93061b2","tid":1469716,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:55:27.000Z